ssen,&quot; he smiled.<br><br>The druid nodded and, noticing a twig in her hair as she did, went back to removing the evidence of her tumble down the hill.<br><br>&quot;Didja get my letter, Mister Khasirath?&quot; she chimed while trying to untangle a particularly well caught thissle from her ponytail.<br><br>Still chuckling, the Tier'Dal nodded. <br><br>&quot;Aye, it is because of you letter that I came to speak with you this eve.&quot; he motioned to the log as he himself took a seat. &quot;Come, we must talk...&quot; <p>Olassen Moonbreeze<BR>The "All Growed Up!" Druid<BR>Daughter of Tunare</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#8E236B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/unowellgoodfelllow.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Nowell Goodfelllow</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(2/25/02 6:41:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=145.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hey Mister Khasirath...!</span><hr size=1> I am sad you didn't mention Uncle Nowell in yer letter, lass.<br><br><br>Nowell Goodfellow <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.showPrevMessage?topicID=145.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.showNextMessage?topicID=145.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=145.topic&index=3><img src=http://www.violentharvest.com/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/fvhbrellfrm2.emailToFriend?topicID=145.topic><img src=http